Dia. 01 Correct Answer
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par White's attaching move at the 1-2 point is the vital point.
\par
\par Black 2 is the best answer and then White 3 is a good move. Black has to play at 4 so it becomes a \cf1\b pae when White takes first\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par
\par
