Dia. 02 Dead Shape
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Against the attachment at \'a1\'e2, if Black answers with 1, he is going to be in big trouble.
\par
\par After White plays at 2, the shape is dead.
\par
\par Black can't cut because of shortage of liberties.
\par }
